[
  {
    "startTime": 14.1,
    "endTime": 16.9,
    "text": "This show was filmed in front of a live studio audience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.8,
    "endTime": 20.900000000000002,
    "text": "Need... furniture!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.4,
    "endTime": 43.199999999999996,
    "text": "I don't know what to do, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.6,
    "endTime": 46.1,
    "text": "You gotta help me; look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.1,
    "endTime": 48.1,
    "text": "Dear Patrick,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.2,
    "endTime": 51.1,
    "text": "Your mom and I are coming out tomorrow for Starfish Day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.2,
    "endTime": 54.2,
    "text": "My parents think I'm dumber than a sack of diapers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.3,
    "endTime": 57.099999999999994,
    "text": "Don't worry, Patrick, I'll be the dummy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.2,
    "endTime": 61.5,
    "text": "When your parents see how dumb I act, they'll think you're the smartest guy ever!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.1,
    "endTime": 65.3,
    "text": "A, B, C, D, E, F, G..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.4,
    "endTime": 67.60000000000001,
    "text": "H, I, J, K, L, M, N, O..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.4,
    "endTime": 70.80000000000001,
    "text": "Should I get the blow horn again, Marty?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.9,
    "endTime": 72.10000000000001,
    "text": "W, X, Y, and Z."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.2,
    "endTime": 74.10000000000001,
    "text": "Hi, Mom, hi, Dad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.6,
    "endTime": 77.19999999999999,
    "text": "Son, you recognized us this time!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.3,
    "endTime": 79.7,
    "text": "Why wouldn't I recognize my own parents?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.8,
    "endTime": 81.6,
    "text": "You never were a bright one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.7,
    "endTime": 82.9,
    "text": "Uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.1,
    "endTime": 85.89999999999999,
    "text": "Well, aren't you gonna show us inside?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 88.1,
    "text": "He probably forgot where it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.2,
    "endTime": 89.2,
    "text": "Oh, I know where⏤"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.3,
    "endTime": 93.39999999999999,
    "text": "Oh, let me lead the way so we don't get lost, huh? Hold hands now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.5,
    "endTime": 97.2,
    "text": "OK, we're almost there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.4,
    "endTime": 101.10000000000001,
    "text": "Let go on three; one, two, three!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.2,
    "endTime": 102.7,
    "text": "Good job!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.8,
    "endTime": 104.39999999999999,
    "text": "- Pats for Patrick!  - Pats for Patrick!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.9,
    "endTime": 110.80000000000001,
    "text": "I'll go get the beverages."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.6,
    "endTime": 118.1,
    "text": "Wow, son, you put the drinks in something this time!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.2,
    "endTime": 122.7,
    "text": "Ah, son, you must've been working all night to put these together for us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.8,
    "endTime": 124.7,
    "text": "- We love you!  - We love you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.3,
    "endTime": 128.8,
    "text": "Hooray! The idiot's here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.9,
    "endTime": 130.5,
    "text": "I mean, I'll get it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.8,
    "endTime": 132.9,
    "text": "What a surprise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.3,
    "endTime": 138.60000000000002,
    "text": "Mom, Dad, meet my neighbor, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.6,
    "endTime": 139.2,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.9,
    "endTime": 140.9,
    "text": "Hello. there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.1,
    "endTime": 142.4,
    "text": "How do you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.5,
    "endTime": 143.2,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.6,
    "endTime": 144.79999999999998,
    "text": "Put her there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.8,
    "endTime": 149.60000000000002,
    "text": "He means shake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.8,
    "endTime": 152.20000000000002,
    "text": "No, SpongeBob, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.3,
    "endTime": 153.60000000000002,
    "text": "Shake hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.8,
    "endTime": 156.3,
    "text": "No, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.4,
    "endTime": 158.3,
    "text": "Grab my dad's hand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.7,
    "endTime": 161.1,
    "text": "Grab it with only one hand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.2,
    "endTime": 162.89999999999998,
    "text": "Good boy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 165.9,
    "text": "Now move your arm up and down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 171.8,
    "text": "So, SpongeBob, do you live nearby?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.9,
    "endTime": 172.3,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.4,
    "endTime": 175.8,
    "text": "No, SpongeBob, show them your house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.8,
    "endTime": 178.8,
    "text": "No, not your blouse!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.9,
    "endTime": 180.70000000000002,
    "text": "Your house!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.8,
    "endTime": 193.5,
    "text": "You know, son, I've always known that when it comes to brightness, well, you're about a 3-watt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.6,
    "endTime": 197.9,
    "text": "But this guy, he's a wet match in a dark cave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 200.5,
    "text": "He makes phone operators seem smart!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.6,
    "endTime": 205.9,
    "text": "But... but, more importantly, son, he's shown me what a sharp, quick-witted boy you've become."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 209.2,
    "text": "I... I feel like I'm really meeting you for the first time!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.3,
    "endTime": 211.4,
    "text": "Isn't that right, Janet?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.5,
    "endTime": 213.5,
    "text": "You bet, Marty!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.4,
    "endTime": 217.4,
    "text": "Janet? Marty?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.5,
    "endTime": 219.5,
    "text": "Who are you people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.6,
    "endTime": 221.29999999999998,
    "text": "Marty, I'm scared."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.5,
    "endTime": 224.6,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.7,
    "endTime": 226.5,
    "text": "Does this lovely couple belong to you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.6,
    "endTime": 230.2,
    "text": "They've been standing outside my house saying, \"Where's Patrick?\" all day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.3,
    "endTime": 231.60000000000002,
    "text": "It's driving me nuts!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.2,
    "endTime": 233.2,
    "text": "Mom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.3,
    "endTime": 234.60000000000002,
    "text": "Dad!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.7,
    "endTime": 240.1,
    "text": "Wow, son, you actually recognized us this time!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.2,
    "endTime": 242.5,
    "text": "And you remembered to get dressed today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.7,
    "endTime": 251.29999999999998,
    "text": "Oh, that's right, honey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.4,
    "endTime": 253.1,
